data.description: Welcome to this light, bright and spacious home featuring an updated kitchen and baths, a three-car garage, Newer synthetic decks in front and out back, plus mature trees and gardens. On the main level, you'll find volume ceilings, ample living and entertaining space, plus a designer kitchen with Silestone counters, high-end appliances, and newer cabinets with soft-close drawers. Just off the dining nook, is a backyard oasis complete with a spacious deck and lush grass. The main level also includes an office/bedroom and there's office potential both upstairs in the loft space and in the fully finished basement. There are five bedrooms total, including a spacious primary retreat featuring a remodeled five-piece ensuite. New roof, new windows, and owned solar. This home is nestled in the established Four Mile Creek neighborhood offering fantastic trails, easy access to Boulder Reservoir, and proximity to both Longmont and Denver. If you want a quiet location and a move-in ready home, this is the one!
